nb well 9x5 cistern river drawbridge plan

Water levers close drawbridge between cistern and well,
and open drawbridge between cistern and river.
Two of these could fit in an 11x11 cell with a walkway
around.

  +lever next to well
  |
  | +cistern
  | |
  ↓ ↓
